          Area schedule · by suite · PDF + XLSX
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure>
        <div class="title-block aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="/projects/suites-plan.webp"
            alt="Lease exhibit showing demised suites and common areas"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="h-full w-full bg-white object-cover object-top"
          />
        </div>
        <figcaption class="mt-3 font-mono text-xs text-ink-muted">
          Lease exhibit · demised suites · PDF + DWG
        </figcaption>
